 assurance, and speed. That creates an incredible tension. You have to be able to rapidly iterate based on knowledge, information, and data collected in the field, which is highly dynamic. It becomes a question of how do you move very quickly, deliver this exquisite capability, and how do you do that with assurance?\"\n\nFull panel in the comments.\n\nAutonomy for the world. The greatest victory requires no war.", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 2, "replyCount": 1, "likeCount": 25, "quoteCount": 1, "viewCount": 2695, "createdAt": "Tue Apr 28 14:07:27 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 1, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2049128363453800841", "displayTextRange": [0, 279], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "shieldaitech", "url": "https://x.com/shieldaitech", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/shieldaitech", "id": "738479913976528896", "name": "Shield AI", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": "Business", "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1458156866844823554/MIXQiJiz_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/738479913976528896/1772753504", "description": "The greatest victory requires no war.\nhttps://t.co/bjaZ1jdDVy", "location": "", "followers": 16439, "following": 282, "status": "", "canDm": false, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Thu Jun 02 21:18:26 +0000 2016", "entities": {"description": {"urls": [{"display_url": "linktr.ee/shieldai", "expanded_url": "https://linktr.ee/shieldai", "indices": [38, 61], "url": "https://t.co/bjaZ1jdDVy"}]}, "url": {"urls": [{"display_url": "shield.ai", "expanded_url": "http://shield.ai", "indices": [0, 23], "url": "https://t.co/0yHa8ufcGh"}]}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 1000, "hasCustomTimelines": false, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 412, "statusesCount": 932, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySen